title: Clay Travis and Buck Sexton Show H1 – Nov 2 2022
itunes:title: Clay Travis and Buck Sexton Show H1 – Nov 2 2022
description:
Biden to address nation tonight as Democrats try to stave off Red Tsunami. Biden goes to Florida, lies about everything. Don't get overconfident, make sure you vote. Buck says, "If we don't get enough votes to make the CNN anchors cry that democracy is ruined, it's not enough." Biden breaks out phony Southern accent. C&B play the worst politician and other Southern accents of all time. Hillary Clinton insults Republican voters again. Buck says we should warn listeners before a Hillary sound bite is played since they are so jarring. Kari Lake goes for the jugular in Arizona race. Clay says, "My point is if you want to win an election, just be normal. So many politicians just can't be."

Follow Clay & Buck on YouTube: https://www.youtube.com/c/clayandbuck
